nodes.text: The Mos Eisley Medical Center was a medcenter located in the city of Mos Eisley, on the Outer Rim world of Tatooine. A medic by the name of Kazen Harn operated out of this facility.
The Mos Eisley Medical Center was a location in the 2003 massively multiplayer online role-playing game Star Wars Galaxies: An Empire Divided, prior to the game's closure on December 15, 2011.
